OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779872675
OL,3,CSearch underway in lake after teenage
OL,4,Cboy goes missing
OL,6,FA major search operation is underway
OL,7,Fto find a teenage boy who reportedly
OL,8,Fwent missing after entering a lake on
OL,9,Fthe hottest day of the year.
OL,11,FEmergency services are in attendance
OL,12,Fat the scene, with police officers
OL,13,Factively searching the area of
OL,14,FPickmere Lake, Cheshire, after the
OL,15,Falarm was raised shortly before 5pm on
OL,16,FTuesday, 27 May.
OL,18,FThe search is being supported by a
OL,19,Fpolice helicopter alongside teams from
OL,20,Fthe Cheshire Fire and Rescue Service.
