OL,3,CSearch underway in lake after teenage
OL,4,Cboy goes missing
OL,6,FMembers of the public are being asked
OL,7,Fto avoid the area entirely while
OL,8,Femergency services carry out their
OL,9,Fwork at the scene.
OL,11,FAnyone with any information is urged
OL,12,Fto contact Cheshire Police as a matter
OL,13,Fof urgency on 101, quoting reference
OL,14,FIML 2336977.
